  "body": "**Precondition:** either recover account with funds or request roETH / STT in simpledapp.eth\r\n\r\n1. Add someone to contacts\r\n2. Open 1x1 chat\r\n3. Click + button at the bottom left\r\n4. click Request transaction\r\n5. Click continue\r\n6. fill in valid amount and click Preview\r\n7. click Request \r\n8. as recipient Click Accept and Send\r\n9. sign with password the transaction\r\n10. click send\r\n\r\n**As result:**\r\n\r\nrequester still see Waiting to accept\r\nsender still see the Accept and Send active\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1439\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-06-16 at 12 40 06\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/122229215-3b125800-cec1-11eb-8cc7-873654c58a26.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
